            "mimeType" : "text\/javascript",
            "size" : 14964,
            "text" : "\n\n\n{\n \"resultCount\":5,\n \"results\": [\n{\n\"episodeUrl\":\"https:\/\/dts.podtrac.com\/redirect.mp3\/pdst.fm\/e\/pfx.vpixl.com\/6qj4J\/pscrb.fm\/rss\/p\/nyt.simplecastaudio.com\/03d8b493-87fc-4bd1-931f-8a8e9b945d8a\/episodes\/aa9519eb-db83-431a-8125-b7af4c0f1ded\/audio\/128\/default.mp3?aid=rss_feed&awCollectionId=03d8b493-87fc-4bd1-931f-8a8e9b945d8a&awEpisodeId=aa9519eb-db83-431a-8125-b7af4c0f1ded&feed=Sl5CSM3S\", \"artworkUrl600\":\"https:\/\/is1-ssl.mzstatic.com\/image\/thumb\/Podcasts211\/v4\/bf\/f9\/87\/bff987a4-d061-d054-32e3-1856beacd24b\/mza_826326965330497418.jpg\/600x600bb.jpg\", \"artistIds\":[], \"collectionViewUrl\":\"https:\/\/itunes.apple.com\/us\/podcast\/the-daily\/id1200361736?mt=2&uo=4\", \"trackViewUrl\":\"https:\/\/podcasts.apple.com\/us\/podcast\/what-weve-learned-from-10-days-of-war\/id1200361736?i=1000754435149&uo=4\", \"artworkUrl60\":\"https:\/\/is1-ssl.mzstatic.com\/image\/thumb\/Podcasts211\/v4\/bf\/f9\/87\/bff987a4-d061-d054-32e3-1856beacd24b\/mza_826326965330497418.jpg\/60x60bb.jpg\", \"trackTimeMillis\":2334000, \"contentAdvisoryRating\":\"Clean\", \"genres\":[{\"name\":\"Daily News\", \"id\":\"1526\"}], \"releaseDate\":\"2026-03-10T09:45:00Z\", \n\"shortDescription\":\"What began as a relentless U.S.-Israeli military assault on Iran has turned into a wider crisis as the disruption of the world’s oil markets spreads beyond the Middle East.\\n\\nEric Schmitt, a national security correspondent for The New York Times, discu\", \"feedUrl\":\"https:\/\/feeds.simplecast.com\/Sl5CSM3S\", \"closedCaptioning\":\"none\", \"collectionId\":1200361736, \"collectionName\":\"The Daily\", \"kind\":\"podcast-episode\", \"wrapperType\":\"podcastEpisode\", \n\"description\":\"What began as a relentless U.S.-Israeli military assault on Iran has turned into a wider crisis as the disruption of the world’s oil markets spreads beyond the Middle East.\\n\\nEric Schmitt, a national security correspondent for The New York Times, discusses what we know about the players involved in the fighting.\\n\\nGuest: Eric Schmitt, a national security correspondent for The New York Times based in Washington.\\n\\nBackground reading: \\n\\n\\n War with Iran has become the world’s latest economic hazard.\\n Follow updates on the fighting in the Middle East.\\n\\nPhoto: Arash Khamooshi for The New York Times\\n\\nFor more information on today’s episode, visit nytimes.com\/thedaily. Transcripts of each episode will be made available by the next workday. \\n\\nSubscribe today at nytimes.com\/podcasts or on Apple Podcasts and Spotify. You can also subscribe via your favorite podcast app here https:\/\/www.nytimes.com\/activate-access\/audio?source=podcatcher. For more podcasts and narrated articles, download The New York Times app at nytimes.com\/app.\\n\\n\\n Hosted by Simplecast, an AdsWizz company. See pcm.adswizz.com for information about our collection and use of personal data for advertising.\", \"country\":\"USA\", \n\"previewUrl\":\"https:\/\/dts.podtrac.com\/redirect.mp3\/pdst.fm\/e\/pfx.vpixl.com\/6qj4J\/pscrb.fm\/rss\/p\/nyt.simplecastaudio.com\/03d8b493-87fc-4bd1-931f-8a8e9b945d8a\/episodes\/aa9519eb-db83-431a-8125-b7af4c0f1ded\/audio\/128\/default.mp3?aid=rss_feed&awCollectionId=03d8b493-87fc-4bd1-931f-8a8e9b945d8a&awEpisodeId=aa9519eb-db83-431a-8125-b7af4c0f1ded&feed=Sl5CSM3S\", \"artworkUrl160\":\"https:\/\/is1-ssl.mzstatic.com\/image\/thumb\/Podcasts211\/v4\/bf\/f9\/87\/bff987a4-d061-d054-32e3-1856beacd24b\/mza_826326965330497418.jpg\/160x160bb.jpg\", \"episodeFileExtension\":\"mp3\", \"episodeContentType\":\"audio\", \"trackId\":1000754435149, \"trackName\":\"What We’ve Learned From 10 Days of War\", \"episodeGuid\":\"f6091b5d-caaf-4ffc-b7e3-bc64977fb3f8\"}, \n{\"episodeUrl\":\"https:\/\/m.pfxes.com\/vcYOs9ob\/traffic.megaphone.fm\/THEDAILYSIGNAL8788380685.mp3\", \"artworkUrl600\":\"https:\/\/is1-ssl.mzstatic.com\/image\/thumb\/Podcasts211\/v4\/93\/6b\/71\/936b71af-121e-dafc-289a-f6f87bbabb8a\/mza_12891591548294721444.jpeg\/600x600bb.jpg\", \"artistIds\":[], \"collectionViewUrl\":\"https:\/\/itunes.apple.com\/us\/podcast\/the-daily-signal\/id1313611947?mt=2&uo=4\", \"trackViewUrl\":\"https:\/\/podcasts.apple.com\/us\/podcast\/victor-davis-hanson-why-americas-most-reliable-ally\/id1313611947?i=1000754554079&uo=4\", \"artworkUrl60\":\"https:\/\/is1-ssl.mzstatic.com\/image\/thumb\/Podcasts211\/v4\/93\/6b\/71\/936b71af-121e-dafc-289a-f6f87bbabb8a\/mza_12891591548294721444.jpeg\/60x60bb.jpg\", \"trackTimeMillis\":647000, \"contentAdvisoryRating\":\"Clean\", \"genres\":[{\"name\":\"Daily News\", \"id\":\"1526\"}], \"releaseDate\":\"2026-03-10T21:00:00Z\", \n\"shortDescription\":\"It's rare for the U.S. to have a capable ally, but Israel is just that.\\n\\n \\n\\nWhile the so-called big powers of NATO don’t have the air capability or the will to cooperate with its allies, Israel does, explains Victor Davis Hanson on today’s episode\", \"feedUrl\":\"https:\/\/feeds.megaphone.fm\/thedailysignal\", \"closedCaptioning\":\"none\", \"collectionId\":1313611947, \"collectionName\":\"The Daily Signal\", \"kind\":\"podcast-episode\", \"wrapperType\":\"podcastEpisode\", \n\"description\":\"It's rare for the U.S. to have a capable ally, but Israel is just that.\\n\\n \\n\\nWhile the so-called big powers of NATO don’t have the air capability or the will to cooperate with its allies, Israel does, explains Victor Davis Hanson on today’s episode of “Victor Davis Hanson: In a Few Words.”\\n\\n \\n\\n“We have a very strong ally in Israel.  We have some unreliable allies in our formal alliance. We should remember that before we start making accusations that the Jews or the Israelis are pulling the strings of American diplomacy and military decision making.”\\n\\n\\n\\n👉Don’t miss out on Victor’s latest videos by subscribing to The Daily Signal today. You’ll be notified every time a new piece of content drops: https:\/\/www.youtube.com\/dailysignal?sub_confirmation=1 \\n\\n\\n\\n👉If you can’t get enough of Victor Davis Hanson from The Daily Signal, subscribe to his official YouTube channel: https:\/\/www.youtube.com\/@victordavishanson7273 \\n\\n\\n\\n👉He’s also the host of “The Victor Davis Hanson Show,” available wherever you prefer to watch or listen. Links to the show and exclusive content are available on his website: https:\/\/victorhanson.com \\n\\n\\n\\nThe Daily Signal cannot continue to tell stories, like this one, without the support of our viewers: https:\/\/secured.dailysignal.com\/ \\nLearn more about your ad choices. Visit megaphone.fm\/adchoices\", \"country\":\"USA\", \"previewUrl\":\"https:\/\/m.pfxes.com\/vcYOs9ob\/traffic.megaphone.fm\/THEDAILYSIGNAL8788380685.mp3\", \"artworkUrl160\":\"https:\/\/is1-ssl.mzstatic.com\/image\/thumb\/Podcasts211\/v4\/93\/6b\/71\/936b71af-121e-dafc-289a-f6f87bbabb8a\/mza_12891591548294721444.jpeg\/160x160bb.jpg\", \"episodeFileExtension\":\"mp3\", \"episodeContentType\":\"audio\", \"trackId\":1000754554079, \"trackName\":\"Victor Davis Hanson: Why America’s Most Reliable Ally Isn’t in NATO\", \"episodeGuid\":\"74bd8f0c-1cb4-11f1-bf2d-13aac8b1fc04\"}, \n{\"episodeUrl\":\"https:\/\/api.fastcast.ai\/audio\/578fda0a-bd22-4d7a-87fa-41b2fb9436e3.mp3\", \"artworkUrl600\":\"https:\/\/is1-ssl.mzstatic.com\/image\/thumb\/Podcasts221\/v4\/11\/21\/81\/1121815e-d409-51fa-0d6e-5756f3b53ac8\/mza_16788476619840616823.jpg\/600x600bb.jpg\", \"artistIds\":[], \"collectionViewUrl\":\"https:\/\/itunes.apple.com\/us\/podcast\/entertainment-celebrity-news-today-2-min-news-the\/id1880937045?mt=2&uo=4\", \"trackViewUrl\":\"https:\/\/podcasts.apple.com\/us\/podcast\/the-a-teams-unfulfilled-trilogy-potential\/id1880937045?i=1000754641878&uo=4\", \"artworkUrl60\":\"https:\/\/is1-ssl.mzstatic.com\/image\/thumb\/Podcasts221\/v4\/11\/21\/81\/1121815e-d409-51fa-0d6e-5756f3b53ac8\/mza_16788476619840616823.jpg\/60x60bb.jpg\", \"trackTimeMillis\":83000, \"contentAdvisoryRating\":\"Clean\", \"genres\":[{\"name\":\"Entertainment News\", \"id\":\"1531\"}], \"releaseDate\":\"2026-03-11T11:02:21Z\", \n\"shortDescription\":\"Director Joe Carnahan laments missed opportunity for The A-Team trilogy, blaming marketing for its underperformance at the box office. Despite earning $177 million worldwide, it struggled against FIFA World Cup and The Karate Kid. Carnahan sees it\", \"feedUrl\":\"https:\/\/feeds.fastcast.ai\/entertainment-news-daily-news-now.xml\", \"closedCaptioning\":\"none\", \"collectionId\":1880937045, \"collectionName\":\"Entertainment & Celebrity News Today | 2 Min News | The Daily News Now!\", \"kind\":\"podcast-episode\", \"wrapperType\":\"podcastEpisode\", \n\"description\":\"Director Joe Carnahan laments missed opportunity for The A-Team trilogy, blaming marketing for its underperformance at the box office. Despite earning $177 million worldwide, it struggled against FIFA World Cup and The Karate Kid. Carnahan sees it as a superhero adventure and regrets not capitalizing on its potential.\\n\\n\\n\\n\\n    Support the show:Get a discount at https:\/\/solipillow.com\/discount\/dnn.\\n\\n\\n\\n\\n    Advertise on DNN:advertise@thednn.ai\\n\\n\\n\\n\\n    This is an automated, high-level news summary based on public reporting.Report issues to feedback@thednn.ai.\\n\\n\\n\\n\\n    View sources & latest updates:https:\/\/sources.thednn.ai\/009b21b8f221b4a0\", \"country\":\"USA\", \"previewUrl\":\"https:\/\/api.fastcast.ai\/audio\/578fda0a-bd22-4d7a-87fa-41b2fb9436e3.mp3\", \"artworkUrl160\":\"https:\/\/is1-ssl.mzstatic.com\/image\/thumb\/Podcasts221\/v4\/11\/21\/81\/1121815e-d409-51fa-0d6e-5756f3b53ac8\/mza_16788476619840616823.jpg\/160x160bb.jpg\", \"episodeFileExtension\":\"mp3\", \"episodeContentType\":\"audio\", \"trackId\":1000754641878, \"trackName\":\"The A-Team's Unfulfilled Trilogy Potential\", \"episodeGuid\":\"578fda0a-bd22-4d7a-87fa-41b2fb9436e3\"}, \n{\"episodeUrl\":\"https:\/\/api.fastcast.ai\/audio\/205c3806-a37e-4fb8-811c-e951bbd011cf.mp3\", \"artworkUrl600\":\"https:\/\/is1-ssl.mzstatic.com\/image\/thumb\/Podcasts221\/v4\/11\/21\/81\/1121815e-d409-51fa-0d6e-5756f3b53ac8\/mza_16788476619840616823.jpg\/600x600bb.jpg\", \"artistIds\":[], \"collectionViewUrl\":\"https:\/\/itunes.apple.com\/us\/podcast\/entertainment-celebrity-news-today-2-min-news-the\/id1880937045?mt=2&uo=4\", \"trackViewUrl\":\"https:\/\/podcasts.apple.com\/us\/podcast\/kate-winslet-eyed-for-lord-of-the-rings-role\/id1880937045?i=1000754642286&uo=4\", \"artworkUrl60\":\"https:\/\/is1-ssl.mzstatic.com\/image\/thumb\/Podcasts221\/v4\/11\/21\/81\/1121815e-d409-51fa-0d6e-5756f3b53ac8\/mza_16788476619840616823.jpg\/60x60bb.jpg\", \"trackTimeMillis\":86000, \"contentAdvisoryRating\":\"Clean\", \"genres\":[{\"name\":\"Entertainment News\", \"id\":\"1531\"}], \"releaseDate\":\"2026-03-11T11:02:30Z\", \n\"shortDescription\":\"Oscar-winning actress Kate Winslet is rumored to join The Hunt for Gollum, playing a supporting female role. Fans speculate she could portray Gilraen, Aragorns mother, potentially showcasing flashbacks of Aragorns early years. Leo Woodall and Anya\", \"feedUrl\":\"https:\/\/feeds.fastcast.ai\/entertainment-news-daily-news-now.xml\", \"closedCaptioning\":\"none\", \"collectionId\":1880937045, \"collectionName\":\"Entertainment & Celebrity News Today | 2 Min News | The Daily News Now!\", \"kind\":\"podcast-episode\", \"wrapperType\":\"podcastEpisode\", \n\"description\":\"Oscar-winning actress Kate Winslet is rumored to join The Hunt for Gollum, playing a supporting female role. Fans speculate she could portray Gilraen, Aragorns mother, potentially showcasing flashbacks of Aragorns early years. Leo Woodall and Anya Taylor-Joy are also reportedly in talks for younger Aragorn and Arwen. This casting buzz marks a full-circle moment for Winslet, who was once considered for Eowyn in the original trilogy. Production begins in New Zealand this May, with more details expected soon.\\n\\n\\n\\n\\n    Support the show:Get a discount at https:\/\/solipillow.com\/discount\/dnn.\\n\\n\\n\\n\\n    Advertise on DNN:advertise@thednn.ai\\n\\n\\n\\n\\n    This is an automated, high-level news summary based on public reporting.Report issues to feedback@thednn.ai.\\n\\n\\n\\n\\n    View sources & latest updates:https:\/\/sources.thednn.ai\/6e49bd30ca2d2eea\", \"country\":\"USA\", \"previewUrl\":\"https:\/\/api.fastcast.ai\/audio\/205c3806-a37e-4fb8-811c-e951bbd011cf.mp3\", \"artworkUrl160\":\"https:\/\/is1-ssl.mzstatic.com\/image\/thumb\/Podcasts221\/v4\/11\/21\/81\/1121815e-d409-51fa-0d6e-5756f3b53ac8\/mza_16788476619840616823.jpg\/160x160bb.jpg\", \"episodeFileExtension\":\"mp3\", \"episodeContentType\":\"audio\", \"trackId\":1000754642286, \"trackName\":\"Kate Winslet Eyed for Lord of the Rings Role\", \"episodeGuid\":\"205c3806-a37e-4fb8-811c-e951bbd011cf\"}, \n{\"episodeUrl\":\"https:\/\/api.fastcast.ai\/audio\/f2c644b2-3d3e-45a6-8988-16ff74ae3d88.mp3\", \"artworkUrl600\":\"https:\/\/is1-ssl.mzstatic.com\/image\/thumb\/Podcasts221\/v4\/11\/21\/81\/1121815e-d409-51fa-0d6e-5756f3b53ac8\/mza_16788476619840616823.jpg\/600x600bb.jpg\", \"artistIds\":[], \"collectionViewUrl\":\"https:\/\/itunes.apple.com\/us\/podcast\/entertainment-celebrity-news-today-2-min-news-the\/id1880937045?mt=2&uo=4\", \"trackViewUrl\":\"https:\/\/podcasts.apple.com\/us\/podcast\/paul-mescal-meets-sir-paul-mccartney-for-beatles-biopic\/id1880937045?i=1000754641112&uo=4\", \"artworkUrl60\":\"https:\/\/is1-ssl.mzstatic.com\/image\/thumb\/Podcasts221\/v4\/11\/21\/81\/1121815e-d409-51fa-0d6e-5756f3b53ac8\/mza_16788476619840616823.jpg\/60x60bb.jpg\", \"trackTimeMillis\":109000, \"contentAdvisoryRating\":\"Clean\", \"genres\":[{\"name\":\"Entertainment News\", \"id\":\"1531\"}], \"releaseDate\":\"2026-03-11T10:52:59Z\", \n\"shortDescription\":\"Paul Mescal, set to portray Sir Paul McCartney in a Beatles biopic, enjoyed a full English breakfast with the legend himself at Londons Regency Cafe. The four-part film, directed by Sam Mendes, marks the first time the Beatles have granted full lif\", \"feedUrl\":\"https:\/\/feeds.fastcast.ai\/entertainment-news-daily-news-now.xml\", \"closedCaptioning\":\"none\", \"collectionId\":1880937045, \"collectionName\":\"Entertainment & Celebrity News Today | 2 Min News | The Daily News Now!\", \"kind\":\"podcast-episode\", \"wrapperType\":\"podcastEpisode\", \n\"description\":\"Paul Mescal, set to portray Sir Paul McCartney in a Beatles biopic, enjoyed a full English breakfast with the legend himself at Londons Regency Cafe. The four-part film, directed by Sam Mendes, marks the first time the Beatles have granted full life and music rights for a scripted movie. Mescal, who has openly admired McCartney, embraced the role, while Barry Keoghan, playing Ringo Starr, admitted nerves meeting the real drummer. The strong cast also includes Harris Dickinson as John Lennon, Joseph Quinn as George Harrison, and Saoirse Ronan as Linda McCartney. Filming began last November and will hit Abbey Road Studios, promising a bingeable theatrical experience.\\n\\n\\n\\n\\n    Support the show:Get a discount at https:\/\/solipillow.com\/discount\/dnn.\\n\\n\\n\\n\\n    Advertise on DNN:advertise@thednn.ai\\n\\n\\n\\n\\n    This is an automated, high-level news summary based on public reporting.Report issues to feedback@thednn.ai.\\n\\n\\n\\n\\n    View sources & latest updates:https:\/\/sources.thednn.ai\/c2176d332b9675a0\", \"country\":\"USA\", \"previewUrl\":\"https:\/\/api.fastcast.ai\/audio\/f2c644b2-3d3e-45a6-8988-16ff74ae3d88.mp3\", \"artworkUrl160\":\"https:\/\/is1-ssl.mzstatic.com\/image\/thumb\/Podcasts221\/v4\/11\/21\/81\/1121815e-d409-51fa-0d6e-5756f3b53ac8\/mza_16788476619840616823.jpg\/160x160bb.jpg\", \"episodeFileExtension\":\"mp3\", \"episodeContentType\":\"audio\", \"trackId\":1000754641112, \"trackName\":\"Paul Mescal Meets Sir Paul McCartney for Beatles Biopic\", \"episodeGuid\":\"f2c644b2-3d3e-45a6-8988-16ff74ae3d88\"}]\n}\n\n\n"
